$ spack add netlib-scalapack %gcc@16 ^netlib-lapack ^openmpi
==> Adding netlib-scalapack %gcc@16 ^netlib-lapack ^openmpi to environment /home/spack/stacks
$ spack add netlib-scalapack %gcc@16 ^netlib-lapack ^mpich
==> Adding netlib-scalapack %gcc@16 ^mpich ^netlib-lapack to environment /home/spack/stacks
